.panel.panel-info
  .panel-heading
    Some of your friends run this category. Click their faces to compare :D
  .panel-body
    - run.user.follows.that_run(run.category).each do |user|
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-4
        .media{style: "margin: .5em 0;"}
          %a.pull-left{href: compare_path(run, user.pb_for(run.category))}
            %img{src: user.avatar, height: 64, width: 64}
          .media-body
            %h4.media-heading= user.name
            = render partial: "shared/time", locals: {time: user.pb_for(run.category).time, show_milliseconds: run.short?}
